oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Human Radio at the Ace of Clubs (proof)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Human Radio (Musical group); Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card proof (blue and red on white) announcing a grand opening extravaganza featuring Tennessee's premier go go dancers on March 15 and 16 and Human Radio (misspelled Haman Radio) on St. Patrick's Day, March 17, at the Ace of Clubs. Poster features woodcuts of the suits in a deck of cards: hearts, spades, diamonds, and clubs.
